{"tid":1728213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果想放棄嘅手足 請入一入黎","createTime":"2019-11-16T18:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T19:15:55.000Z","uid":68026,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b9763c10c57853bd570c45b574e6cd87a9e046cf","tid":1728213,"uid":68026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCiwwB2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCiwwB2.png&h=07536c02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>如果想放棄嘅時候 請望望依張相<br />\n諗返究竟大家嘅初衷係咩<br />\n只有不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰 先能夠取得最後勝利</em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>勇武手足們</strong>：請繼續堅持你相信嘅 我地相信你地做野有底線有目標 唔係班仆街口中嘅暴徒 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>和理非手足們</strong>：請繼續堅守 「不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰」大原則 繼續堅守五大訴求 繼續文宣工作 <br />\n<br />\n大家請一定要保持理性獨立思考 五毛自然退散<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></em></strong>"},{"pid":"9594addecc3c1c444136768a4973d6cec26ca849","tid":1728213,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:54:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de2001ef027d2a50a4c6474956385a3e46fbab43","tid":1728213,"uid":68026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:54:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c0886b8ee375ca6b3068e90901c55921b1eef11","tid":1728213,"uid":68026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:54:30.000Z","msg":"人手推post"},{"pid":"21d182489bba88636a0016c532013d6933c08adb","tid":1728213,"uid":68026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:54:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe882d3640c8a1f8316fa3abb2dd7cbdede67ffe","tid":1728213,"uid":68026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:54:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"038ed317fe38a7af65378302c70e15c1c13cfb26","tid":1728213,"uid":68026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:55:33.000Z","msg":"頂撚住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99e159c8cfe